		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />This isn't even necessarly, what I meant is that if you have a 32kb EPROM and a UNROM devcart, puting the 32kb EPROM on the UNROM devcart has a 6/7 probability to work. It won't work if you are unlucky enough so that bank 7 is swapped at $8000-$bfff at power up.

		

